  "message": "chore(conformance): regenerate support matrix after dlfcn/inet6/context nativization\n\nUpdate support_matrix_maintenance_report.v1.json to reflect 49 symbols\nmoving from GlibcCallThrough to Implemented status (323->274 call-through,\n2066->2115 implemented). Affected families include:\n\n- argp_* (6 symbols): argp_error, argp_failure, argp_help, argp_parse,\n  argp_state_help, argp_usage\n- inet6_opt_*/inet6_option_*/inet6_rth_* (19 symbols): full IPv6\n  extension header API\n- ucontext (4 symbols): getcontext, makecontext, setcontext, swapcontext\n- rcmd/rexec/ruserok family (9 symbols): remote shell utilities\n- obstack_* (3 symbols): obstack_free, obstack_printf, obstack_vprintf\n- ns_name_* (4 symbols): DNS name compression helpers\n- parse_printf_format, dl_iterate_phdr, dladdr, iruserok, iruserok_af\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
